(reconstruction fidelity, and transferability should be modeled and evaluated together rather) Tj
T*
(than as loosely connected local improvements. Our entry point is to organize prior work) Tj
T*
(around the missing synthesis between road priors, spatiotemporal dynamics, and robustness to) Tj
T*
(irregular or shifted observations. This framing gives the next methodological step a clearer) Tj
T*
